## Architecture Pattern

Route → Service → Prisma (three-layer separation)

- **Routes** (`src/routes/`): HTTP parsing, status codes, response formatting
- **Services** (`src/services/`): Business logic, validation, orchestration
- **Prisma** (`prisma/`): Data access, migrations, schema

